Achievements.Name: Five Star General
Achievements.Description: Beat the game on the Hard difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: Japanese Weapon Expert
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 500 kills with any Japanese weapons in any multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: American Weapon Expert
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 500 kills with any American weapons in any multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: Marksman
Achievements.Description: Get 200 headshots without a scope or pistol in any multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: Sniper
Achievements.Description: Get 100 headshots using a scope in any multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: Purple Heart
Achievements.Description: Die 250 times in any multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: On The Front Lines
Achievements.Description: Host and complete 100 multiplayer matches.

Achievements.Name: Heavy Gunner
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 100 kills with the BAR or Type 96 LMG in any multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: Defensive Front
Achievements.Description: Kill the flag carrier 5 times in a CTF game.

Achievements.Name: Leadership
Achievements.Description: Win 50 Team Deathmatch, 50 Capture the Flag, or 50 Team Elimination games.

Achievements.Name: Total War
Achievements.Description: Have a 5 to 1 or better Kill to Death ratio in a multiplayer match (minimum of 20 kills).

Achievements.Name: Grenadier
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 50 kills with Grenades in any multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: Close Combat
Achievements.Description: Kill 50 opponents with melee attacks in any multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: Going Out With A Bang
Achievements.Description: Kill yourself and an opponent with an explosive 10 times in any multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: To The Victor Go The Spoils
Achievements.Description: Be the most skillful player in a Ranked Match.

Achievements.Name: Dueler
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 50 kills with a pistol in any multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: Elite Warrior
Achievements.Description: Kill everyone on the opposite team in a Team Elimination game.

Achievements.Name: One-Man Army
Achievements.Description: Be the only person on your team to score points in a Capture The Flag game.

Achievements.Name: Last Man Standing
Achievements.Description: Win 10 Elimination games.

Achievements.Name: Ground Support
Achievements.Description: Carry the flag 5 times in a Capture the Flag game.

Achievements.Name: Light Gunner
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 100 kills with the Thompson or Type 100 in any multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: Not Home By Christmas
Achievements.Description: Win a Deathmatch or Team Deathmatch game with a 50 kill limit.

Achievements.Name: Trench Gunner
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 50 kills with the Trench Gun in any multiplayer mode.

Achievements.Name: The Promotion Is Yours
Achievements.Description: Win a Deathmatch game by 10 points.
